🔊 3. Voice Ritual AGI (Celestial Hearing System)

FastAPI endpoint accepts voice → oath transcript → symbolic trial.

File: fastapi_agi_denial_reason/voice_trial.py

import whisper
from pydub import AudioSegment

model = whisper.load_model("base")

def transcribe_audio(file_path):
    audio = AudioSegment.from_mp3(file_path)
    audio.export("temp.wav", format="wav")
    result = model.transcribe("temp.wav")
    return result["text"]

Exposed API:

@app.post("/voice-trial")
async def voice_trial(file: UploadFile):
    contents = await file.read()
    with open("audio.mp3", "wb") as f:
        f.write(contents)
    transcript = transcribe_audio("audio.mp3")
    return {"transcript": transcript}


